{"tid":1578764,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"已經諗到對策921","createTime":"2019-09-18T09:10:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-18T09:28:21.000Z","uid":128569,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"544459bfcf466a4d07aa0ae3adcbe2b56578b222","tid":1578764,"uid":128569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T09:10:20.000Z","msg":"呢幾日大家唔好痴文宣住 <br />\n係921朝 大家落去痴啲超能膠落啲文宣度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到時就痴尻佢地隻手 拆到咁撚爽呀拿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adf63b705d589128d0bd889deed93d9e0bfda104","tid":1578764,"uid":128569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T09:11:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"934476e0b01763c026f70f3288f99e6978282a28","tid":1578764,"uid":140326,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T09:14:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DybagsD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDybagsD.png&h=4fa62521&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n新聞頭條"},{"pid":"fbe9859b53b22b8e4def48ba859466eeb20ad17a","tid":1578764,"uid":128569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"934476e0b01763c026f70f3288f99e6978282a28","tid":1578764,"uid":140326,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T09:14:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DybagsD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDybagsD.png&h=4fa62521&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n新聞頭條"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T09:15:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁癲呀ching"},{"pid":"d4d3b8e237187a38a03fe7c87f6832e4778c18f9","tid":1578764,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T09:15:46.000Z","msg":"【9.23~9.27】全球「反共」聯軍來了我帶路！快閃式萬國「民主」旗號召世界<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eccnjS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eccnjS</a><br />\n<blockquote><br />\n由於香港身為東道主倘若因為任何原因而令到遊行人數小得難睇, 是不理想的！<br />\n<br />\n同埋我寧願10.1國殤打到拆天就最好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />當然大家請記著呢日唔是End-game<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 由美帝反共眾議員可以見到場戰爭並非一朝一夕<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 失去所有勇武運動將難以持續<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家講到星期日9.29是全球性<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 單靠香港人文宣團隊twitter retweet比當地人是難以收到巨大宣傳效益<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />！<br />\n<br />\n唯有無比juicy<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />方法去呼喚他國人民, 同埋件事夠juicy<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />外國媒體先會幫你免費頭版<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【9.23~9.27】全球「反共」聯軍來了我帶路！<br />\n集合時間：1930~2000<br />\n遊行時間：2000~終點和平散去 (預計9點前行到遮打即龍頭散去)<br />\n舉行日期：9月23日至9月27日晚上快閃式遊行<br />\n遊行路線：修頓球場 至 遮打花園<br />\n注意事項：遊行完就即時由中環遮打盡快散去！不起衝突！人小就行行人路<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n衣著：遊行時黑色, 前往及離開時非黑色<br />\n快閃遊行目的：號召全球「反共」聯軍同時響應9.29大遊行, 盡可能與香港同步舉行！<br />\n利申：是次遊行屬自發性質, 沒有不反對通知書<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講到反共你走去申請唔好傻啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我主張每晚均可見到頭60名民主國度<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n只要有60位手足舉60支旗個畫面已經夠晒Juicy<br />\n首先你話該國家一直龜縮有咩撚用,舉嚟把撚啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但是9.29反共大遊行號召目標是各國人民,<br />\n如果我地真是連續一星期舉民主國家國旗, 當地右翼會相當自豪<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />,<br />\n同埋每晚我地可以twitter開放檢討比各國人民知道其國旗在香港揚起以打倒中共</blockquote>"},{"pid":"ede2e51bb18ac25dd6ef8baa8c54e754ffeb363a","tid":1578764,"uid":140326,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T09:16:21.000Z","msg":"仲921朝？你920晚好做啦，隔離話左加刀片，針，石灰粉