 />\n集合時間：1930~2000<br />\n遊行時間：2000~終點和平散去 (預計9點前行到遮打即龍頭散去)<br />\n舉行日期：9月23日至9月27日晚上快閃式遊行<br />\n遊行路線：修頓球場 至 遮打花園<br />\n注意事項：遊行完就即時由中環遮打盡快散去！不起衝突！人小就行行人路<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n衣著：遊行時黑色, 前往及離開時非黑色<br />\n快閃遊行目的：號召全球「反共」聯軍同時響應9.29大遊行, 盡可能與香港同步舉行！</strong></span><br />\n利申：是次遊行屬自發性質, 沒有不反對通知書<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講到反共你走去申請唔好傻啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我主張每晚均可見到頭60名民主國度<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n只要有60位手足舉60支旗個畫面已經夠晒Juicy<br />\n首先你話該國家一直龜縮有咩撚用,舉嚟把撚啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但是9.29反共大遊行號召目標是各國人民,<br />\n如果我地真是連續一星期舉民主國家國旗, <span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>當地右翼會相當自豪<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span>,<br />\n同埋每晚我地可以twitter開放檢討比各國人民知道其國旗在香港揚起以打倒中共</blockquote>"},{"pid":"8b919cc87fd77b834cc457763cde2d2dac39a843","tid":1578764,"uid":266289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T09:26:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">幫推啦喂</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kgdgb4b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fkgdgb4b.jpg&h=8361ea83&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6ec76f0c1141dbb4ad4cda08003b8c73fbc47b9d","tid":1578764,"uid":33907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T09:27:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n返歸瞓覺啦 廢青<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd40960095676247a9729c7afa203e4f56dd6abe","tid":1578764,"uid":33907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a247105225178b813e4954f0721f80dd2c9f4